videos.description: Quentin Goodin finds Trevon Bluiett open behind the arc for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bluiett knocks down first points on 3-pointer

videos.description: Xavier's Trevon Bluiett drives down the lane and converts on the easy layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Bluiett breezes by the defense for easy layup

videos.description: Xavier's Trevon Bluiett continues to remain aggressive in the first half as he knocks down his second 3-pointer of the game.
videos.headline: Bluiett knocks down long 3 ball

videos.description: J.P. Macura finds Kerem Kanter open in the corner for his first 3-pointer of the season.
videos.headline: Xavier's ball movement leads to Kanter 3-pointer

videos.description: Quentin Goodin finds Tyrique Jones open in the paint for the loud two-handed dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Xavier's Jones hangs on rim after emphatic dunk

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jacob Evans pulls up from mid-range and knocks down the shot for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Evans earns and-1 on tough jumper
